ChangeLog:

nxbuilder-3.5.0-3

- Fixed TR11I02632. The NX Builder setup procedure uses the keyword "TYPE" for
  storage engine settings. However, starting from version 5, MySQL could not
  support anymore that keyword and require keyword "ENGINE" instead. In this case
  NX Builder setup procedure fails to create tables into the Builder db.

nxbuilder-3.5.0-2

- Fixed TR09I02608. When the user chooses "available area"  in the display 
  options list, the correspondent key, namely Resolution, is always set to
  800x600 in the nx session file and the session cannot be started at available
  area.

- Improved print of embeddable code in configuration section

nxbuilder-3.5.0-1

- Opened the 3.5.0 branch based on nxbuilder-3.4.0-2.

- Updated copyright to year 2011.

nxbuilder-3.4.0-2

- Updated license-info file.

nxbuilder-3.4.0-1

- Opened the 3.4.0 branch based on nxbuilder-3.3.0-2.

- Updated copyright to year 2011.

nxbuilder-3.3.0-2

- Implemented FR09G02265. Now the NX Builder gives the possibility to
  configure the session for activating the multi-monitor support in
  the NX Client for Windows.

nxbuilder-3.3.0-1

- Opened the 3.3.0 branch based on nxbuilder-3.2.0-2

nxbuilder-3.2.0-2

- Fixed TR07F02083. NX Builder is able to manage correctly all settings
  when the Administrator has enabled a connection via HTTP proxy with
  user/password authentication method.  

nxbuilder-3.2.0-1

- Implemented FR03F02027. Improved the embeddable code generated
  by NX Builder in the Configuration interface.

- Fixed TR03F02022. Added control on path string for Single Application
  for RDP session.

- Opened the 3.2.0 branch based on nxbuilder-3.1.0-4.

nxbuilder-3.1.0-4

- Improved Input management in Modify Server procedure.

- Improved function to check access permissions.

- Improved function to detect if input has a valid value.

- Fixed TR03F02016 and TR03F02017. Settings for VNC and RDP sessions
  are now stored in the proper format. 

nxbuilder-3.1.0-3

- Changed function to check access permission.

- Created function for detecting valid input value to avoid Sql 
  injection attack.

- Implemented FR02F02005. NX Builder can generate a nxsession
  file for running a Single Application in a RDP Session. 

- Fixed TR02F02003. Changed the display number format of the remote
  VNC server like requested by NX Node.

nxbuilder-3.1.0-2

- Updated the NoMachine copyright notices. 

- Fixed Notice and Warning messages displayed into the Web page
  when running NX Builder. This solves #TR01F01997. 

nxbuilder-3.1.0-1

- Opened the 3.1.0 branch based on nxbuilder-3.0.0-24. 

nxbuilder-3.0.0-24

- Removed domain field control in Windows RDP settings when it is 
  empty. This solves TR12E01961.  

- Added function to manage bottom toolbar in the case no items are 
  listed. This solves TR10E01923.

- Changed setup procedure to manage default value for MySql 5.0.2. 
  This solves TR11E01933.  

- Changed setup errors management. Added new button named Detail in 
  the administrator's interface, to display content of the log file.
  This solves TR10E01922.

- Implemented FR12E01960. Added the possibility to disable use of 
  DirectDraw when creating session files. 

nxbuilder-3.0.0-23

- Implemented FR08E01828. NX Builder User and NX Builder Guest are
  redirected to the Server List page upon login. 

- Implemented FR08E01826. NX Builder Administrator can decide the
  default link type and he can decide also if to show or not the 
  link type menu to NX Builder User and NX Builder Guest. 

- Fixed MODEM link displayed to the NX Builder Administrator. This 
  solves TR08E01827.

- Changed number of characters for NX Builder User's username. This
  solves TR08E01825.

nxbuilder-3.0.0-22

- Modified Css for IE for Win. This solves TR07E01771.

nxbuilder-3.0.0-21

- Improved setup function in order to support PHP configuration when 
  register_global directive is disabled.  

- Defined some variables in order to avoid notice message in html tag 
  when PHP html_errors and error_reporting directive is enabled.

- Removed PHP close tag in Top.php. This solves TR07E01744.

nxbuilder-3.0.0-20

- Improved procedure to upgrade database. Now setup script is abled to 
  upgrade his own database.
  
- Improved position preview layer in configuration section when the 
  height exceeds the resolution of the screen. 
    
- Corrected wrong settings in create session file referred to unix
  display.     

nxbuilder-3.0.0-19

- Removed buttons "add session", "add server" and "add user" from top
  toolbar. Now this button has moved in bottom toolbar.

- Changed toolbar and page background.

- Improved javascript function to manage position of the draggables 
  layers.

- Changed screenshot in configuration template.

- Improved functions to manage new settings display for windows, vnc, 
  unix and shadow sessions. 

- Introduced custom JPEG quality in window and vnc display setting. 

- Changed output mode for desktops and applications sessions in 
  server list template.

nxbuilder-3.0.0-18

- Implemented new management of Rdp and Jpeg compression in Unix,
  Windows and Vnc display setting.

- Modified Create Session file.

- Modified error and info messages position.

- Changed layout structure "Disable display of this server via Web"
  in AddServer and ModifyServer.

nxbuilder-3.0.0-17

- Fixed some css rules for Safari, Konqueror, IE 5.2 for Mac, Firefox 
  for Linux abd Mac. 

- Changed several javascript functions for assign sessions in add
  and modify user. Now these functions are cross-browser. 

- Improved Ajax function to manage Administrator user sessions.

- Changed some labels and messages in setup.

nxbuilder-3.0.0-16

- Changed NX sessions management in user list and modify user for 
  NX Builder Administrator. 

- Changed function to generate embeddable code.

- Changed preview template.

nxbuilder-3.0.0-15

- Modified function for Guest user authentication. Now, access mode 
  to NX Server, is stored in a browser sessions variables.

- Corrected php code that produces notice messages when PHP directive 
  "error_reporting" is setted to 'ALL'.
  
- Modified rules to set background image in toolbar in default css
  file. Now the image starts from right to left.  

- Added javascript function in configuration user interface. This  
  function sets status for button that sets bold/normal label style. 
  
- Implemented function to manage the case when builder.cfg not found.

- Added messages when servers list or sessions list are empty.  
    
- Implemented a function to delete old custom css.

- Implemented function to detect if javascript is enabled.  

- Changed default toolbar and page background image. 

- Modified color picker structure.

- Changed Copyright in all files.

- Added function to create NX Session file in the embedded code used
  to generate server list page for the Guest Builder User.

- Implemented new administration interface to give the possibility 
  to the administrator to customize the appearance of the Web page, 
  deployed for the NX Guest Builder user and generated by extracting 
  the embeddable code.This implements FR05E01684. 
  
- Changed and implemented new function for logging off in Toolbar.

nxbuilder-3.0.0-14

- Modified tab menu in add/modify session, based on css rules.

- Added new fields in skinSetting table to manage tab menu colors.

- Modified javascript function to manage server display settings.

nxbuilder-3.0.0-13

- Update lincense info.

- Implemented function in the Setup procedure that allows to recover
  images associated to servers and/or sessions in case of upgrade of 
  NX Builder. The procedure allows to specify the source path from 
  which the images have to be retrieved. 

- Added logging function to track the Setup procedure.

- Added workaround to allow to support css cache in IE.

- Implemented system to manage css cache.

- Changed some css rules to allow for setting custom background and 
  colors through the administrator interface.

- Implemented FR05E01684. Created function to give the possibility 
  to select the NX Builder appearance through a new administration 
  interface. 

nxbuilder-3.0.0-12

- Implemented function to manage customization of the NX Builder
  appearance based on settings stored in the database.
  
- Added table to store the NX Builder appearance settings.

- Modified Setup procedure to manage the table needed for storing 
  the NX Builder appearance settings.
  
- Modified structure of the user list Web page to display information
  in a clearer way. 

nxbuilder-3.0.0-11

- Improved Setup procedure to handle compatibility with a previous
  version of the database and create backup of the original database.

- Improved function to create database and configuration file. 

- Added layer to set display resolution and link type in the session 
  list Web page either for the administrator and the Builder User.

- Modified css properties to set label in all panels.

- Improved function to suspend access to the server or replacing it 
  with an alternative text.
  
nxbuilder-3.0.0-10

- Improved function to upload images and create new categories for 
  sessions.
  
- Improved function for printing php and html code used to generate
  server list page for the Guest Builder User.    

- Modified toolbar and session list structure.

nxbuilder-3.0.0-9

- Implemented Ajax function to show sessions assigned to the user
  according to the NX server selected among the list of servers that
  are associated to that user.   

- Improved errors management for sessions, servers and users. 

- Implemented DB functions for managing updates to sessions, servers 
  and users. 

- Implemented administrator interface for managing updates to users,
  sessions, and servers.

- Added functions to delete sessions, servers and users.

- Changed function to handle upload of image files to be associated
  to either servers and sessions.

- Added workaround to fix the Internet explorer 6 'min-width bug'. 

- Implemented function and administrator interface to assign sessions 
  on a per-server basis to the user.

- Implemented javascript function to pass options between the selects 
  used for associating sessions to the user, either in the add and 
  modify user procedures.

nxbuilder-3.0.0-8

- Replaced all the images shipped by the NX Builder package with new 
  png images.

- Changed errors management system. 

- Implemented function to preserve values already set in the form 
  fields. When an error occurs, preventing data from being inserted
  in the DB, values already set in the form fields are not lost.

nxbuilder-3.0.0-7

- Implemented function to display preview of the server list page 
  in a draggable layer. 

- Implemented FR05E01683. Created function to extract embeddable code 
  that generates the server list page to be deployed on the Web for 
  any Guest Builder User.  

nxbuilder-3.0.0-6

- Modified javascript file to load not common css properties for each 
  browser.

- Implemented css file to manage common style sheet properties.

- Improved administrator interface to provide draggable panels for
  enhanced session configurations.

- Improved error management in login system.

- Implemented function to disable/enable slide-bar.

- Implemented slide-bar on Display Settings panels for unix and windows
  session configuration.   

nxbuilder-3.0.0-5

- Implemented function to enable or disable administrative buttons 
  in the NX Builder toolbar according to the profile of the logged-in 
  user. 

- Implemented new authentication system based on browser sessions.

nxbuilder-3.0.0-4

- Implemented javascript function to use transparent layers in order
  to disable the toolbar, the tab-bar and the menu-lists when the 
  panel options are opened. 

- Added a workaround to fix the IE 'box-model bug'.

- Added new css rules.

- Implemented a javascript function to switch Display Settings panel
  according to the selected desktop type.

- Implemented workaround to support transparent layer also when the
  browser is Internet Explorer. These transparent layers are needed
  to disable elements in the Web page. 

- Added displaySettings table to the DB to manage Display Settings 
  configured for unix, RDP and VNC sessions. 

nxbuilder-3.0.0-3

- Added new toolbar and background images.

- Re-implemented function to create session file according to the 
  enhanced session configuration allowed by the new administrator
  interface.

- Changed database functions to manage the new tables. 

- Added tables rdpServers, httpProxy, fontServers, customOptions, 
  vncServers, xdmOptions to the database in order to improve the 
  management of the sessions.
  
nxbuilder-3.0.0-2

- Improved javascript function to manage sessions assignment on a
  per-user basis by using Ajax function.

- Implemented new interfaces for adding and listing NX Builder user.

- Added workaround to allow Internet Explorer to handle properly  
  Z-index for windowed element.  

nxbuilder-3.0.0-1

- Improved usability of the user interface. Thanks to the use of Ajax 
  functions, instead of refreshing all the Web page, only sections
  that have been modified are re-loaded.

- Improved the structure of the NX Builder backend. 

- Added function to disable/enable toolbar.

- Added new function to retrieve server and session details. 

- Improvements to the user interface templates.

- Implemented FR03E01653. This extends the possibility to deploy 
  specific applications on a per-user basis.

- Implemented FR02E01641. This gives the possibility to make enhanced
  session configuration via the NX Builder administrator's interface
  providing the same level of configuration offered by the NX Client
  GUI.
  
- Opened the 3.0.0 branch based on the 2.1.0-5 version.

nxbuilder-2.1.0-5

- Changed the LICENSE file to state that the software is only made
  available under the version 2 of the GPL.

- Added file COPYING.

nxbuilder-2.1.0-4

- Updated license-info file. 

- Improved the db configuration procedure in order to update data
  and structure of an older database. 

- Added new apache directives in the conf file.
  
nxbuilder-2.1.0-3

- Improved add and modify server procedures in order to give the
  possibility of hiding any of the servers listed in the Web page.
  This version solves TR08D01459.
  
- According to the new modifications, have been added new fields in
  the servers table and in the Connection file.
  
- Modified the graphics of server list for guest and server list 
  pages.

nxbuilder-2.1.0-2

- Modified some queries in order to keep the relations between ser-
  vers, sessions and users in case that MySQL backend doesn't support 
  innodb. This solves TR08D01458.

- Added possibility of updating a command specified in the modify 
  server page. This solves TR08D01457.

- Modified the configure guest page in order to show the application
  name instead of the command.
  
- Added some checks on the name of the application in javascript 
  function.  

- Updated the links to the NX Client download.

nxbuilder-2.1.0-1

- Opened the 2.1.0 branch based on the 2.0.0-23 version.

nxbuilder-2.0.0-23

- Modified the application command parsing and storing to allow the
  options use.

