- Added new field in the sessions table in order to assign a name to
  a command.
  
- According to the new modifications to database, the Connection fi-
  le, the add server procedure and the update server procedure have
  been changed.
  
- Added info button in Session List Guest page to visualize server 
  information.

- Modified the graphical appearance of some pages.

- Removed some unused code.

nxbuilder-2.0.0-21

- Fixed a problem on Configure Guest page to store the sessions in
  the select list each time the form is submitted.
  
